propsSchema.description:
Displays an image from a URL, base64 data URL, or signable storage path. Useful for showing pasted images, charts, or any visual asset.

## Example

```json
{
  "type": "image",
  "props": {
    "src": "https://example.com/map.png",
    "alt": "Map preview",
    "objectFit": "contain"
  }
}
```
